{"tid":492080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"教你如何增加VR AV臨場感","createTime":"2017-12-07T07:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T08:53:35.000Z","uid":10958,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a22b98f8c64fe7f9f0c46b9a88be8799cfb113","tid":492080,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hi-auntie.com/2017/12/06/vrav/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhi-auntie.com%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2Fvrav%2F&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0bacd050\" target=\"_blank\">https://hi-auntie.com/2017/12/06/vrav/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n據《nuwton》報導，編輯セブ山介紹一個讓大家觀看VR AV片時有臨場感的方法&hellip; 就是去按摩院，一邊做推油按摩一邊看VR AV片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_97af0725a1b43972618622cd0f6ff509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_97af0725a1b43972618622cd0f6ff509.jpg&h=b953ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n編輯セブ山親自去按摩院試看VR AV<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_f4b794a4ba4b1c2f6f24fa976a85c01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_f4b794a4ba4b1c2f6f24fa976a85c01a.jpg&h=ac5fbe12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVR AV片中是這個樣子<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_7fac74e78cf96bb4d54966cc19c3114b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_7fac74e78cf96bb4d54966cc19c3114b.jpg&h=a65191db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但是實際上是這樣子<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_85e37dac7b23f107014d415f235c2243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_85e37dac7b23f107014d415f235c2243.jpg&h=061d8caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好 High 好爽的樣子<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_88c011d93d84ed19ae2cbedfcdef97de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_88c011d93d84ed19ae2cbedfcdef97de.jpg&h=cf3d3bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想要對片中的女優出手<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_59a1486f4102eefb78be6fe351212d99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_59a1486f4102eefb78be6fe351212d99.jpg&h=a643a621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n忍不住出手了，但實際上是摸到男按摩師<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_867a93b7f90632ec138d2bd6e04196b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_867a93b7f90632ec138d2bd6e04196b5.jpg&h=d0acb031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按摩師會無言的看著你<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_2efed98de8ff19897b8abbca7d9cef63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_2efed98de8ff19897b8abbca7d9cef63.jpg&h=73954cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按摩師非常專業<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_4f5881d012296776426ec7fe957dfcc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_4f5881d012296776426ec7fe957dfcc2.jpg&h=304a7854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完真係好爽<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_1642fd7fbb2b6d9050837869e5ea3270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_1642fd7fbb2b6d9050837869e5ea3270.jpg&h=99b5a665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n編輯セブ山拿下VR眼鏡後&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://auntienews.files.wordpress.com/2017/12/640_e6d6b99c2d1a8d60f8e35b0d0c98ce7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauntienews.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F12%2F640_e6d6b99c2d1a8d60f8e35b0d0c98ce7c.jpg&h=178cd3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任務完成 !!!"},{"pid":"4280720f7ff390c0cea2cad66c9bfa7e1ee465e5","tid":492080,"uid":161243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"想嘔"},{"pid":"18f46059ca4fabd7b451c56f0bf63bf61aaba148","tid":492080,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"教你如何增加VR AV臨場感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/489191/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/489191/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bb597888edfe8f2ee2579806436da62de56d07","tid":492080,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"男人先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989551c02e185fe70c2dbdc16137e35d1a4a9a4e","tid":492080,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"iMOM"}]}